name: Vintage Paper Pack
description:
I have searched the globe to put together these packs!

Each pack varies slightly and the one you will receive may not be exactly the same as those in the picture however, I endeavour to keep them as similar as possible.

In these HUGE pack you will receive 40+ vintage (and a few contemporary) papers and ephemera.

Each pack includes but is not limited to:

Aussie Drink Labels
Tickets
Recipe Pages
Bingo Cards
Kraft Paper
Tags
Children's storybook pages
Game cards
School/Library Ephemera
Maps
Trading Cards
Pattern Pieces
Dictionary Pages
Foreign Language Text (German, Arabic, Japanese, French etc.)
*New addition - double sided music sheet

Grab yourself a bag full of inspiration for all your crafting projects.
